Transforms the target's skin into that of the dead...tough, ugly and<br>
resistant to all manner of damage.  Because of the stiffening of limbs, a<br>
targets combat effectiveness and ability to move is somewhat effected. <br>
Under the mantle of the dead, it is also wise not to attempt to enter<br>
good-aligned towns that generally take exception to the walking dead<br>
seeking goods and services.<br>
